Job Details
One of the leading Brokerage House in AbuDhabi is looking for Egyptian Sales Manager with min 10 years of experience in Selling of Egyptian property, good knowledge of handling the renting, selling of Apartment. well versed with GCC countries. will be handling a team of sales and real estate small dealers across UAE and GCC countries.
